wikipedia_page.main: George Samuel Drissell (born 20 January 1999) is an English cricketer. He made his first-class debut for Gloucestershire in the 2017 County Championship on 6 August 2017. He made his List A debut for Gloucestershire in the 2018 Royal London One-Day Cup on 6 June 2018.
